{"tid":2016125,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 要來打破常規，今年 WWDC 將以 iPhone 鏡頭做直播！","createTime":"2020-05-14T07:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T08:00:49.000Z","uid":12628,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b12e420639ff4e83641f3fb5de172977be6dd9c9","tid":2016125,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:26:17.000Z","msg":"近期，彭博社記者 Mark Gurman 報導，稱 Apple 計劃在今年 WWDC 上只依靠 iPhone 進行流媒體直播。在上週 Apple 就已經宣布了 WWDC 2020 將於 6 月 22 日以線上形式舉辦，原因正是受到各地的武漢肺炎疫情影響。<br />\n<br />\nApple 之所以打算用 iPhone 來用做直播，其實是有「前科」的。在 4 月份時，美國廣播公司介紹了由 45 人組成的劇組是如何進行本季《American Idol》的錄製。當時經過 TechCrunch 的證實，得知團隊是依靠 iPhone 和配套的配件錄製的，讓人不禁讚歎 iPhone 的拍攝能力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3w4mbu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3w4mbu.jpg&h=1af2c54f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，Apple 官方向 TechCrunch 的查詢作出回應，自信的表示了 iPhone 擁有業內領先的相機拍攝能力。原文是這麼描述的：「我們知道，人們在家中觀看自己喜歡的節目時，都會依賴 iPhone，我們很高興能與《American Idol》團隊一起參與到這一過程中來。」<br />\n<br />\niPhone 的拍攝能力其實也向來受到肯定，全球很多大大小小的直播、微電影等都是由 iPhone 所拍攝製作出來。也許，世上只有 DxOMark 這家相機評測機構，認為 iPhone 的拍攝能力很差勁罷了。<br />\n<br />\n即將於 6 月 22 日舉行的 WWDC 20 年度開發者大會，Apple 將會對外展示最新的一系列操作系統，包括旗下最多人使用的 iOS 14，還有全新的 iPadOS、macOS、tvOS 以及 watchOS 等等，是一場值得期待的發布會。"},{"pid":"0950804d2bca7e919b5b05ff5e0344a8dabbf5e7","tid":2016125,"uid":186431,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QejBciL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQejBciL.jpg&h=04058c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e20f8737f4ed36512115deaae81125a39a6f8c","tid":2016125,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:28:43.000Z","msg":"Link <a href=\"https://qooah.com/2020/05/13/apple-iphone-broadcast-wwdc-2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2020%2F05%2F13%2Fapple-iphone-broadcast-wwdc-2020%2F&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7qkErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=d9a2e545\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2020/05/13/apple-iphone-broadcast-wwdc-2020/</a>"},{"pid":"f238d6c3f67d909aabebf0cdfde908be6687b616","tid":2016125,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:51:27.000Z","msg":"無敵！。！"},{"pid":"5dc6266da5044c8b6fb72d87bff22020e36152d2","tid":2016125,"uid":82587,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"抄三星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd26ad9eb626d7913ea8ae6cf79bbff27699a49d","tid":2016125,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5dc6266da5044c8b6fb72d87bff22020e36152d2","tid":2016125,"uid":82587,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"抄三星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff3843485c84639ba14c918156e700a506cffe4","tid":2016125,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:00:49.000Z","msg":"連登講拍片 = nothing"}]}